\
### **2. KI\uc0\u7870 N TR\'daC \u272 \u7872  XU\u7844 T: B\u7892  SUNG T\u7846 NG "METABOLISM LAYER"**\
\
\uc0\u272 \u7875  t\u7893  ch\u7913 c c\'e1c "axitamin" m\u7897 t c\'e1ch khoa h\u7885 c, em \u273 \u7873  xu\u7845 t th\'eam m\u7897 t t\u7847 ng ki\u7871 n tr\'fac m\u7899 i, n\u7857 m gi\u7919 a **Infrastructure Layer** v\'e0 **Core Engine Layer**, g\u7885 i l\'e0 **METABOLISM LAYER** (T\u7847 ng Chuy\u7875 n H\'f3a). T\u7847 ng n\'e0y s\u7869  cung c\u7845 p c\'e1c d\u7883 ch v\u7909  n\u7873 n t\u7843 ng, c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'ed nh\u432  **h\u7879  ti\'eau h\'f3a, tu\u7847 n ho\'e0n v\'e0 b\'e0i ti\u7871 t** c\u7911 a c\u417  th\u7875 .\
\
**C\uc0\u7845 u tr\'fac \u273 \u7873  xu\u7845 t:**\
\
```\
src/\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472 \u9472  core/ (c\'e1c engine c\u7889 t l\'f5i: events, smartlink, memory, snapshot...)\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472 \u9472  metabolism/ (T\u7846 NG M\u7898 I \'96 ch\u7913 a c\'e1c "axitamin")\
\uc0\u9474    \u9500 \u9472 \u9472  processors/          # UDP \'96 b\u7897  x\u7917  l\'fd d\u7919  li\u7879 u \u273 a n\u259 ng\
