**T\uc0\u432 \u417 ng t\'e1c v\u7899 i c\'e1c th\'e0nh ph\u7847 n kh\'e1c:**\
\
- **Quantum Defense Cell** s\uc0\u7869  s\u7917  d\u7909 ng c\'e1c d\u7883 ch v\u7909  t\u7915  Metabolism Layer \u273 \u7875 :\
  - Chu\uc0\u7849 n h\'f3a d\u7919  li\u7879 u \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o t\u7915  c\'e1c c\u7843 m bi\u7871 n (nh\u7901  `normalizers`).\
  - Ph\'e2n t\'edch log t\uc0\u7921  ph\u7909 c h\u7891 i \u273 \u7875  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\'e1c pattern b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng (`anomaly-detector`).\
  - S\uc0\u7917  d\u7909 ng ML \u273 \u7875  c\u7843 i thi\u7879 n \u273 \u7897  ch\'ednh x\'e1c c\u7911 a vi\u7879 c ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n "v\u7853 t l\u7841 " (`text-classifier` c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t request c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0 bot d\u7921 a tr\'ean n\u7897 i dung).\
  - N\uc0\u7841 p c\'e1c plugin m\u7899 i \u273 \u7875  m\u7903  r\u7897 ng kh\u7843  n\u259 ng nh\u7853 n di\u7879 n (v\'ed d\u7909  plugin nh\u7853 n di\u7879 n lo\u7841 i t\u7845 n c\'f4ng m\u7899 i).\
\
- **QNEU (ch\uc0\u7885 n l\u7885 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean)** s\u7869  quan s\'e1t hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  c\u7911 a c\'e1c "axitamin" n\'e0y:\
  - M\uc0\u7897 t processor x\u7917  l\'fd CSV t\u7889 t s\u7869  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ghi nh\u7853 n v\'e0 t\u259 ng t\u7847 n su\u7845 t s\u7917  d\u7909 ng.\
  - M\uc0\u7897 t plugin b\u7883  l\u7895 i s\u7869  b\u7883  \u273 \'e0o th\u7843 i (\u273 i\u7875 m s\u7889  gi\u7843 m).\
  - C\'e1c `permanent_nodes` c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng enzyme \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t hi\u7879 u qu\u7843 , \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u432 u gi\u7919  v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n.\
\
- **UEI (n\'e3o b\uc0\u7897 )** ra l\u7879 nh s\u7917  d\u7909 ng metabolism layer khi c\u7847 n x\u7917  l\'fd d\u7919  li\u7879 u th\'f4 ho\u7863 c khi ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\'f4i tr\u432 \u7901 ng thay \u273 \u7893 i (v\'ed d\u7909 : khi c\'f3 file \u273 \u7883 nh d\u7841 ng m\u7899 i, n\'e3o b\u7897  g\u7885 i `plugin.manager` \u273 \u7875  t\u7843 i b\u7897  x\u7917  l\'fd t\u432 \u417 ng \u7913 ng).\
\
