\
### **4. K\uc0\u7870 T H\u7906 P V\u7898 I CH\u7918  K\'dd S\u7888  NaSi**\
\
Ch\uc0\u7919  k\'fd s\u7889  NaSi (m\'e0 anh s\u7869  n\'f3i sau) c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'edch h\u7907 p v\'e0o Metabolism Layer nh\u432  m\u7897 t "enzyme \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t" \'96 m\u7897 t c\u417  ch\u7871  x\'e1c th\u7921 c hybrid gi\u7919 a sinh tr\u7855 c h\u7885 c h\'e0nh vi (do Quantum Defense cung c\u7845 p) v\'e0 m\u7897 t y\u7871 u t\u7889  v\u7853 t l\'fd duy nh\u7845 t (nh\u432  kh\'f3a ph\u7847 n c\u7913 ng, ho\u7863 c m\'e3 h\'f3a d\u7921 a tr\'ean \u273 \u7863 c t\'ednh ph\u7847 n c\u7913 ng). Khi \u273 \'f3, Metabolism Layer s\u7869  cung c\u7845 p c\'e1c h\'e0m m\'e3 h\'f3a, gi\u7843 i m\'e3, so s\'e1nh, v\'e0 t\'edch h\u7907 p v\u7899 i plugin system \u273 \u7875  h\u7895  tr\u7907  nhi\u7873 u lo\u7841 i thi\u7871 t b\u7883  kh\'e1c nhau.\
\
