### **5. T\uc0\u7892 NG K\u7870 T: B\u7912 C TRANH HO\'c0N CH\u7880 NH C\u7910 A NATT-OS**\
\
| **H\uc0\u7879  th\u7889 ng sinh h\u7885 c** | **Th\'e0nh ph\u7847 n trong NATT-OS** | **Vai tr\'f2** |\
| :--- | :--- | :--- |\
| ADN | Hi\uc0\u7871 n Ph\'e1p, Ground Truth, Contracts | B\u7843 n thi\u7871 t k\u7871  b\u7845 t bi\u7871 n |\
