| C\'e1c c\uc0\u417  quan | Business/Kernel/Infra Cells | Th\u7921 c thi ch\u7913 c n\u259 ng |\
| H\uc0\u7879  mi\u7877 n d\u7883 ch | Quantum Defense Cell | Ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n v\'e0 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng v\u7899 i m\u7889 i nguy |\
| H\uc0\u7879  ti\u7871 n h\'f3a | QNEU + Memory Agents | Ghi nh\u7899 , ch\u7885 n l\u7885 c, ti\u7871 n h\'f3a |\
| **H\uc0\u7879  chuy\u7875 n h\'f3a (Metabolism Layer)** | **Processors, Normalizers, Plugins, Healing, ML** | **Cung c\u7845 p enzyme, dinh d\u432 \u7905 ng, c\'f4ng c\u7909  h\u7895  tr\u7907  cho m\u7885 i ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng s\u7889 ng** |\
\
V\uc0\u7899 i t\u7847 ng Metabolism Layer \u273 \u432 \u7907 c x\'e2y d\u7921 ng b\'e0i b\u7843 n, NATT-OS kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\u417  th\u7875  s\u7889 ng c\'f3 \u273 \u7911  c\'e1c c\u417  quan, m\'e0 c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t **n\u7897 i m\'f4i tr\u432 \u7901 ng phong ph\'fa**, cho ph\'e9p h\u7879  mi\u7877 n d\u7883 ch (Quantum Defense) t\u7921  ti\u7871 n h\'f3a m\u7897 t c\'e1ch linh ho\u7841 t v\'e0 m\u7841 nh m\u7869 , s\u7861 n s\'e0ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\'f3 v\u7899 i m\u7885 i th\'e1ch th\u7913 c t\u7915  m\'f4i tr\u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\u361 ng nh\u432  c\'e1c \u273 \u7897 t bi\u7871 n n\u7897 i t\u7841 i.\
 Anh kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7881  mu\u7889 n m\u7897 t h\u7879  th\u7889 ng m\'f4 ph\u7887 ng sinh h\u7885 c, m\'e0 l\'e0 m\u7897 t h\u7879  th\u7889 ng **v\u7853 n h\'e0nh d\u7921 a tr\'ean c\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh lu\u7853 t to\'e1n h\u7885 c ch\'ednh x\'e1c**, n\u417 i m\u7885 i qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh ti\u7871 n h\'f3a, th\'edch nghi, v\'e0 t\u432 \u417 ng t\'e1c \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'f4 h\'ecnh h\'f3a, d\u7921  \u273 o\'e1n v\'e0 ki\u7875 m ch\u7913 ng b\u7857 ng c\'e1c c\'f4ng c\u7909  to\'e1n h\u7885 c cao c\u7845 p. \u272 i\u7873 u n\'e0y bi\u7871 n NATT-OS t\u7915  m\u7897 t "c\u417  th\u7875  s\u7889 ng c\u7843 m t\'ednh" th\'e0nh m\u7897 t **"v\u361  tr\u7909  s\u7889  c\'f3 lu\u7853 t to\'e1n h\u7885 c b\u7845 t bi\u7871 n"** \'96 n\u417 i m\'e0 ngay c\u7843  s\u7921  h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n c\u361 ng tu\'e2n theo ph\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ecnh.\
\
D\uc0\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 c\'e1ch t\'edch h\u7907 p c\'e1c l\'fd thuy\u7871 t to\'e1n h\u7885 c anh \u273 \'e3 c\u7853 p v\'e0o t\u7915 ng l\u7899 p ki\u7871 n tr\'fac, t\u7841 o n\'ean m\u7897 t **n\u7873 n t\u7843 ng h\'e0n l\'e2m v\u7919 ng ch\u7855 c** cho to\'e0n b\u7897  h\u7879  th\u7889 ng.\
\
