## **T\'cdCH H\uc0\u7906 P V\'c0O KI\u7870 N TR\'daC HI\u7878 N T\u7840 I**\
\
T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c l\'fd thuy\u7871 t tr\'ean s\u7869  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hi\u7879 n th\u7921 c h\'f3a d\u432 \u7899 i d\u7841 ng c\'e1c module trong **Metabolism Layer** v\'e0 **Quantum Defense Cell**, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i cung c\u7845 p d\u7919  li\u7879 u cho **QNEU** \u273 \u7875  ti\u7871 n h\'f3a.\
\
**Metabolism Layer** m\uc0\u7903  r\u7897 ng:\
- `math/` \'96 th\uc0\u432  m\u7909 c ch\u7913 a c\'e1c thu\u7853 t to\'e1n to\'e1n h\u7885 c:\
  - `replicator-dynamics.ts` \'96 c\uc0\u7853 p nh\u7853 t t\u7847 n su\u7845 t pattern.\
  - `nash-equilibrium.ts` \'96 t\'ecm c\'e2n b\uc0\u7857 ng Nash cho c\'e1c t\u432 \u417 ng t\'e1c.\
  - `lyapunov.ts` \'96 t\'ednh s\uc0\u7889  m\u361  Lyapunov t\u7915  chu\u7895 i th\u7901 i gian.\
  - `fisher-info.ts` \'96 t\'ednh th\'f4ng tin Fisher.\
  - `persistent-homology.ts` \'96 ph\'e2n t\'edch t\'f4-p\'f4 d\uc0\u7919  li\u7879 u.\
  - `error-correction.ts` \'96 m\'e3 Hamming, m\'e3 h\'f3a \uc0\u273 \u7841 i s\u7889 .\
\
**Quantum Defense Cell** s\uc0\u7869  g\u7885 i c\'e1c module n\'e0y \u273 \u7875 :\
- D\uc0\u7921  \u273 o\'e1n tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i t\u432 \u417 ng lai (dynamical systems).\
- Ph\'e1t hi\uc0\u7879 n c\u7845 u tr\'fac b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng trong SmartLink (topology).\
- \uc0\u272 \'e1nh gi\'e1 \u273 \u7897  \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh c\u7911 a c\'e1c chi\u7871 n l\u432 \u7907 c ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng (game theory).\
\
**QNEU** s\uc0\u7917  d\u7909 ng k\u7871 t qu\u7843  \u273 \u7875 :\
- C\uc0\u7853 p nh\u7853 t `frequency_imprints` theo replicator dynamics.\
- X\'e1c \uc0\u273 \u7883 nh c\'e1c `permanent_nodes` d\u7921 a tr\'ean ti\'eau chu\u7849 n ESS.\
- Ghi nh\uc0\u7853 n c\'e1c attractor m\u7899 i.\
\
