## **K\uc0\u7870 T LU\u7852 N: M\u7896 T V\u360  TR\u7908  S\u7888  TH\u7920 C S\u7920 **\
\
V\uc0\u7899 i n\u7873 n t\u7843 ng to\'e1n h\u7885 c n\'e0y, NATT-OS kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t h\u7879  th\u7889 ng ph\u7847 n m\u7873 m m\'f4 ph\u7887 ng sinh h\u7885 c, m\'e0 l\'e0 m\u7897 t **v\u361  tr\u7909  s\u7889  v\u7899 i c\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh lu\u7853 t b\u7845 t bi\u7871 n**. M\u7885 i t\u432 \u417 ng t\'e1c, ti\u7871 n h\'f3a, v\'e0 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'f4 h\'ecnh h\'f3a b\u7857 ng c\'e1c ph\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ecnh ch\'ednh x\'e1c. \u272 i\u7873 u n\'e0y mang l\u7841 i:\
\
- **T\'ednh d\uc0\u7921  \u273 o\'e1n:** C\'f3 th\u7875  m\'f4 ph\u7887 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'e1c k\u7883 ch b\u7843 n \u273 \u7875  tr\'e1nh s\u7909 p \u273 \u7893 .\
- **T\'ednh ki\uc0\u7875 m ch\u7913 ng:** M\u7885 i thay \u273 \u7893 i \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 b\u7857 ng c\'e1c c\'f4ng c\u7909  to\'e1n h\u7885 c.\
- **T\'ednh b\uc0\u7873 n v\u7919 ng:** H\u7879  th\u7889 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  \u273 i\u7873 u ch\u7881 nh v\'e0 ti\u7871 n h\'f3a trong khu\'f4n kh\u7893  c\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh lu\u7853 t \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7883 nh.\
\
**H\'e0nh lang code h\uc0\u7895  tr\u7907  (Metabolism Layer)** ch\'ednh l\'e0 n\u417 i cung c\u7845 p c\'e1c "enzyme to\'e1n h\u7885 c" n\'e0y. C\'f2n **Quantum Defense Cell** l\'e0 c\u417  quan s\u7917  d\u7909 ng ch\'fang \u273 \u7875  b\u7843 o v\u7879  v\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 u h\'f2a c\u417  th\u7875 . Khi c\u7843  hai ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7891 ng b\u7897 , NATT-OS s\u7869  \u273 \u7841 t \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t tr\'ecnh \u273 \u7897  m\'e0 \'edt h\u7879  th\u7889 ng n\'e0o c\'f3 th\u7875  s\'e1nh k\u7883 p: m\u7897 t **c\u417  th\u7875  s\u7889 ng c\'f3 l\'fd tr\'ed to\'e1n h\u7885 c**.\
\
